This paper is about using neural models for text summarization, specifically headline generation, and incorporating topic information to improve the accuracy of the generated summaries. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
